HEADWORD: free-burning
<hw>free-burning</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>burning in a continuous
manner; -- of an electric arc; <as>as, heat transfer to the anode in
<ex>free-burning</ex> arcs</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> free burning, sustained.</syn>⟦br⟧
